{
  "stem": "5313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one morning they ask for volunteers, about 100 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was one of them who volunteered to get out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they put us in a side of a hill to dig a hole.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we didn't know what that really meant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we dig the hole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And late afternoon, you know, we went back to the factory, which I said it was a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we find out that-- But started to get dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they started to ask for volunteers again, 200, 300 people at a time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we find out they took them to the hill site where we was digging up and they started to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They started to kill them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that started to go on and on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we heard the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I happened to go up in a chimney where I find out what's happening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I came down and I tell my friends, you know, what's going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And at that time--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They tried to kill us, you know, so they don't know where-- probably they get an order not to bring us further up, so probably they give us an order to get rid of us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they couldn't kill every one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can tell you that-- that when we get walking to the next, we was maybe only a few thousand left already.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And probably they tried not to, during the day, to see, you know, what they doing, so they did every killing during the night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had that much, that when we was walking back, we had one chance that we can do the people who cannot walk further, they can put-- get down on their knee, you know, and they shoot them right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
